sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant AuthMW as Authentication<br/>Middleware
    participant QuotaMW as Quota<br/>Middleware
    participant OAuth as OAuth2/JWKS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Router as Inference Router
    participant Provider as Provider Resolver
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant VectorDB as PostgreSQL+pgvector<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Tools as External Tools<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request
        Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
        Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
        AuthMW->>OAuth: GET /.well-known/jwks.json<br/>TLS 1.2+ (cached)
        OAuth-->>AuthMW: Public keys (JWKS)
        AuthMW-->>Server: User attributes (claims)
        Server->>QuotaMW: Check rate limit
        QuotaMW-->>Server: OK (1000 req/day auth)
        Server->>Router: Route to inference provider
        Router->>Provider: Resolve provider (remote-vllm)
        Provider->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS, Bearer Token
        vLLM-->>Provider: SSE: data: {"choices":[...]}
        Provider-->>Router: Stream chunks
        Router-->>Server: AsyncGenerator
        Server-->>Client: SSE: text/event-stream<br/>x-trace-id header
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,VectorDB: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector IO + Inference)
        Client->>Server: POST /v1/tool-runtime/rag-tool/query<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
        AuthMW-->>Server: OK
        Server->>QuotaMW: Check rate limit
        QuotaMW-->>Server: OK

        Note over Server,vLLM: Step 1: Generate embeddings
        Server->>vLLM: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>(via inference provider)
        vLLM-->>Server: Embedding vector

        Note over Server,VectorDB: Step 2: Query vector store
        Server->>VectorDB: SELECT with pgvector similarity<br/>5432/TCP, Password auth
        VectorDB-->>Server: Relevant chunks

        Note over Server,vLLM: Step 3: Generate response with context
        Server->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with retrieved context)
        vLLM-->>Server: Completion response

        Server-->>Client: JSON response with citations
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Tools: Flow 3: Agent Turn with Tool Execution
        Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, SSE stream
        Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
        AuthMW-->>Server: OK

        Note over Server,vLLM: Step 1: Initial LLM call
        Server->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with tool definitions)
        vLLM-->>Server: tool_call: {"name":"web_search","args":{...}}

        Note over Server,Server: Step 2: Safety check (inline)
        Server->>Server: Run safety shield<br/>(in-process)

        Note over Server,Tools: Step 3: Execute tool
        Server->>Tools: GET https://api.tavily.com/search<br/>TLS 1.2+, API key
        Tools-->>Server: Search results

        Note over Server,vLLM: Step 4: Final LLM response
        Server->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with tool results)
        vLLM-->>Server: Final response

        Server-->>Client: SSE: agent turn events<br/>(tool_call, tool_result, completion)
    end
